descriptionHtml:
Can be installed with NMM/MO.

Manual installation: Place file in SKSE-Plugins-CharGen-Presets

Mods needed:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] (and it's requirements)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28363/?]Beards[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes of Beauty[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73605/?]Ixum's Tattoos

[/url]Outfits used:

[url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/forums/topic/5916-daren-bless-online-armor-for-sam-v11/#comment-128920]Daren for SAM[/url] (belt, pants and boots)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20094/?]Desperado Attire[/url] (hat)

Use: 

Open Racemenu (showracemenu in console), select race Nord. Press the preset tab in Racemenu and load preset "Ixum_SethBullock" 

Bodymod used in pics: [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/files/]SAM[/url] with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59944/?]Ixum's Texture replacer
[/url][url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/forums/topic/5947-hdt-butt-breast-belly-bounce-for-sam-v11/]HDT fo[/url][url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/forums/topic/5947-hdt-butt-breast-belly-bounce-for-sam-v11/]r SAM[/url]
Skeleton used [url=http://www.loverslab.com/topic/25971-xp32-maximum-skeleton-extended/]XPSME[/url]
